OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780251071
OL,3,CFour men rescued from flooded Laos
OL,4,Ccave as search continues for two
OL,5,Cmissing
OL,7,FThe villagers reportedly entered the
OL,8,Fcave last week to look for valuable
OL,9,Fminerals before being trapped by flash
OL,10,Fflooding. Another man escaped in time
OL,11,Fand alerted the authorities to the
OL,12,Fseven left behind.
OL,14,FFlood waters, which had blocked their
OL,15,Fexit, had receded enough to allow them
OL,16,Fto leave with divers who had been
OL,17,Ftaking the villagers food and drink
OL,18,Fsince they were found on Wednesday,
OL,19,FLao organisation Rescue Volunteer for
OL,20,FPeople said on its Facebook page.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
