OL,3,CFour men rescued from flooded Laos
OL,4,Ccave as search continues for two
OL,5,Cmissing
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FFriday's operation to free the first
OL,13,Fman took about 30 minutes, according
OL,14,Fto rescue organisations. Videos showed
OL,15,Fthe moment he emerged from the water
OL,16,Falongside a diver, catching his breath
OL,17,Fbefore struggling to crawl through a
OL,18,Fnarrow, water-logged passage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
