OL,3,CFour men rescued from flooded Laos
OL,4,Ccave as search continues for two
OL,5,Cmissing
OL,7,FThe men had been supplied with water,
OL,8,Fsoft food and foil blankets to keep
OL,9,Fthem warm, although videos shot inside
OL,10,Fthe cave suggested that their
OL,11,Fconditions continued to deteriorate.
OL,13,FRescue teams from Laos and
OL,14,Fneighbouring Thailand were joined by
OL,15,FJapanese and Malaysian colleagues.
OL,16,FIndonesian, French and Australian
OL,17,Fspecialists also reportedly arrived at
OL,18,Fthe site in a rugged area in the
OL,19,Fcentral province of Xaisomboun, about
OL,20,F120 kilometers (75 miles) north of the
OL,21,Fcapital, Vientiane.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
